| publisher = Sina
| date = 2006
| language = Simplified Chinese
| url = http://ent.sina.com.cn/f/m/jackybaby/comments/more.html
| accessdate = 2007-08-28}}</ref> The film topped the Chinese box office in [[October 2006]] and grossed over [[United States dollar|US$]]20 million worldwide, even though it was not released in most [[Europe]]an and [[North America]]n countries.<ref name = Cbx>{{cite web
| title = Rob-B-Hood tops the October box office, grossing 90 million (宝贝抢钱9000万《宝贝计划》票房雄踞10月影市) 
