  | title = Information of Rob-B-Hood
  | publisher = Golden Screen Cinemas Malaysia
  | date = 2006-09-29
  | url = http://www.gsc.com.my/version2/movies/movies.asp?search=robbhood
  | accessdate = 2007-08-23 }}</ref> ''Rob-B-Hood'' was released in [[Japan]] on [[7 April]], [[2007]].<ref name = JP>{{cite web
  | title = Official Website of Rob-B-Hood in Japan
  | date = 2007-04-07
  | url = http://www.projectbb.jp/top.html
  | language = Japanese
  | accessdate = 2007-08-23 }}</ref> [[Greece]] remains the only [[Europe|European]] country in which ''Rob-B-Hood'' was released, on [[13 February]], [[2007]].<ref name = GR>{{cite web
  | first = Pantelis
  | last = Maurommatis
  | title = Review of Rob-B-Hood
  | date = 2007-02-13
