  | language = Greek
  | accessdate = 2007-08-23 }}</ref> ''Rob-B-Hood'' is rated [[Hong_Kong_motion_picture_rating_system#Ratings_System|IIA]] in Hong Kong (unsuitable for children), G in Singapore and U in Malaysia.<ref name = "Twitch">{{cite web
| last = Martin
| first = Peter
| title = Rob-B-Hood Review
| publisher = Twitch
| date = 2007-01-22
| url = http://twitchfilm.net/archives/008799.html
